newsitem.title: USA: U.S. jet fuel trade comatose ahead of Memorial Day.
newsitem.headline: U.S. jet fuel trade comatose ahead of Memorial Day.

text.p: Jet fuel differentials were talked at slightly higher levels Friday, though no barrels were reported traded in extremely thin action ahead of the three-day Memorial Day holiday.
Activity in the market remained extremely quiet throughout the day, players said, with prompt 54-grade jet barrels in the Gulf bid at about 0.60 cent under the June NYMEX futures.
Rateable June barrels of 54-grade in the Gulf were talked between about 1.00 to 0.75 cent under the July NYMEX, market watchers said.
